text: chaur anak( mou ham meat) pol tha tae knongchamnaom mcheasa robsa puok anak mean anaknea del ach changaoulobangheanh tow rk karpit noh? chaur anak pol tha meante a l laoh te del ach changaoul bangheanh tow rk karpit ban . tae anak del changaoulobangheanh tow rk kar pitchea anak del trauv ke korp tam da pitabrakd ryy anak del min ach changaoulobangheanh meante trauvkar ke changaoulobangheanh vea vinh noh? tae puok anak mean banhhea avei? tae puok anak vinichchhy yeang dauch me d ch
